### 创建一笔账单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 99.50,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "remark": "请客吃饭",
  "merchant": "海底捞火锅",
  "date": "2026-03-14"
}

### 查询所有账单
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transactions

### 获取预算列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/budgets

### 设置预算 (收入分类 - 工资收入)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "工资收入",
  "limit": 10000.00
}

### 设置预算 (支出分类 - 餐饮)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "餐饮",
  "limit": 2000.00
}

### 更新预算 (支出分类 - 餐饮)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "餐饮",
  "limit": 2500.00
}

### 删除预算
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/budgets/餐饮

